{"tid":2088944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英內政大臣彭黛玲：這是香港傷感的一天","createTime":"2020-07-01T12:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T16:36:24.000Z","uid":53844,"like":213,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3d2f81c893938a45ebbee899a6e5976718e139","tid":2088944,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"Sad day for Hong Kong. China's decision to enact this legislation constitutes a clear &amp; serious breach of the Joint Declaration.<br />\n<br />\nUK will not look the other way. We will uphold our historic responsibilities &amp; we will proceed to honour our commitment to those holding BNO status.<br />\n<br />\n這是香港傷感的一天。<br />\n<br />\n中國頒布這項立法的決定明顯地嚴重違反了《聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n英國不會選擇袖手旁觀。<br />\n<br />\n我們將秉承我們的歷史責任，並將繼續履行對英國國民（海外）的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pritipatel/status/1278298758183354368?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpritipatel%2Fstatus%2F1278298758183354368%3Fs%3D21&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=add6f7e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpritipatel%2Fstatus%2F1278298758183354368%3Fs%3D21&h=e3c1949e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pritipatel/status/1278298758183354368?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"ac744a697eff40422745bbbd09c1ee9c159a8efb","tid":2088944,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0887c2feb9a9929bb1ed3970d9f09b9f3a79ef7","tid":2088944,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da438825c56d5ae3415cf5d36aa03f23f6a2ad52","tid":2088944,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /